item.title: Keepass
item.description: Master password cracking keepass2john key.kdbx > hash # With a key file keepass2john -k key.png key.kdbx > hash kpcli # Open kdbx kpcli --kdb key.kdbx # Open kdbx with a key file kpcli --key key.png --kdb key.kdbx # List all passwords find . # Show password (e.g. #0) show -f 0 # Export attachment (e.g. #0) attach 0 Ref: Download kpcli
